i oni kontroliraju medije.

889
00:43:09,305 --> 00:43:10,445
Vlada izlazi

890
00:43:10,465 --> 00:43:14,005
s takvim
smiješno objašnjenje.

891
00:43:14,025 --> 00:43:15,045
Vau!

892
00:43:15,065 --> 00:43:17,105
To vrijeđa
inteligencija</font>

893
00:43:17,125 --> 00:43:18,125
ovih vrlo

894
00:43:18,145 --> 00:43:19,205
vjerodostojan
svjedoci.

895
00:43:19,225 --> 00:43:20,225
Bilo je
osjećaj za

896
00:43:20,245 --> 00:43:21,385
